//Recommendation: Supplemental diagnostics

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 10 of Cardiac MRI

When I select 'CT Thorax' checkbox
Then 'Contrast enhanced' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'CT Abdomen' checkbox
Then 'Contrast enhanced' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'MR Abdomen' checkbox
Then 'Contrast enhanced' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Myocardial scintigraphy/Myocardial SPECT' checkbox
Then 'With stress' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Follow-up cardio MRT' checkbox
Then '3 Months' radio button is enabled
And '6 Months' radio button is enabled
And '12 Months' radio button is enabled
